==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Officially
<hw>Of*fi"cial*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>By the proper
officer; by virtue of the proper authority; in pursuance of the special
powers vested in an officer or office; <as>as, accounts or reports
<ex>officially</ex> verified or rendered; letters <ex>officially</ex>
communicated; persons <ex>officially</ex> notified.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Officialty</ent>⟦br⟧
